channel.title: 525 compiler errors when trying to add shop? At least take a look!
channel.description:
I'm trying to transfer shops from one source that has them to one that was never set up to have shops... I got these errors:
[code]Compiling rs2hd/*.java src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:19: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: package com.rs2hd.util import com.rs2hd.util.ShopManager; ^ src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:31: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: class com.rs2hd.model.World private ShopManager shopManager; ^ src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:339: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: class com.rs2hd.model.World public ShopManager getShopManager() { ^ src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:299: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: class com.rs2hd.model.World shopManager = new ShopManager(); ^ 4 errors rs2hd/*.java complete src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:19: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: package com.rs2hd.util import com.rs2hd.util.ShopManager; ^ src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:31: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: class com.rs2hd.model.World private ShopManager shopManager; ^ src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:339: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: class com.rs2hd.model.World public ShopManager getShopManager() { ^ src\com\rs2hd\model\World.java:299: cannot find symbol symbol : class ShopManager location: class com.rs2hd.model.World shopManager = new ShopManager(); ^ 4 errors[/code]
Anyone please help?
Thanks Ghostly150
